,{"pid":"32b60796e3a1b9077e2d3cf9410269ca9c090a58","tid":520432,"uid":162772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"有震但冇肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3dabce4d5c20aa3828257360a00072d60693bc","tid":520432,"uid":19448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:33:26.000Z","msg":"好震但冇肥<br />\n利申：考巴士牌"},{"pid":"6d443d4ab548b16a37384e04949d805eb878b4e7","tid":520432,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"震到pk。冇肥"},{"pid":"66b65427599ecb17ae47518af799bd31159478e3","tid":520432,"uid":93224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dc3e77856f2219ad092577a74c489987c58d988","tid":520432,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"緊張就震"},{"pid":"c8ae33243648a9e65b2943ed62275d9609a36db8","tid":520432,"uid":2673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"我自己係十拿九穩嗰啲嚟，但有時稍為少少凍個人都會好易震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學車有次連上兩堂連調頭泊位嗰啲，跟著第二堂嗰陣有一次隻左腳係震到un腳咁。啊Sir以為我緊張叫我放鬆啲唔使咁緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後考試嗰陣都十一、二月驚會凍到腳震鬆咗極力子，好彩考嗰陣又無陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eecb1f36a9e06b6ccdf4125524bcd1958eb0aea","tid":520432,"uid":73715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又係震到好似啲古惑仔un腳咁<br />\n幾驚吊吊下鬆左<br />\n好在最後都pass左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317c8e568ae0a5f57a561579412fb3a8ec01d12a","tid":520432,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"好多年前嘅事<br />\n<br />\n練車無震<br />\n<br />\n考牌貓王<br />\n<br />\n好很記得<br />\n<br />\n考第一次勁震<br />\n<br />\n第二次好少少，都係有震"},{"pid":"cc1903a07d71309940c1d2e2f6baa14a47d9ba69","tid":520432,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"714183de2a942ee77e0cb403dcaaa56398f1cca1","tid":520432,"uid":125759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"考泊位調頭個時隻左腳吊極力子時震到跳舞咁，出到街反而冇再震。關唔關緊張事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T05:00:06.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣 調頭震到死埋火 以為hi博肥緊 之後行街平常心就無震 結果pass左"},{"pid":"ec6de7dd6ba621aad5a7678550d95544565f0ad8","tid":520432,"uid":66654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"打少啲丁"},{"pid":"9e5ee1fb54ee1b519abc3f5732141f9c718f4f8a","tid":520432,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"當年我又係震到un腳咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實吊極力子掉頭泊位嗰時，<br />\n可唔可以踩住個break煞車？"},{"pid":"ed1c0faee79a09d41fc79fe8169a16e6502091e0","tid":520432,"uid":72735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T05:15:22.000Z","msg":"考老電<br />\n去office報到條仆街唔肯比平時架車(A)我<br />\n咁我唯有揸(B)去熱身<br />\n熱2下都係覺得唔對路<br />\n駕院d車部部都差好遠，尤其係d摩擦點同煞車靈敏度<br />\n咁我返去話要換車，佢比(C)我<br />\n呢架仲衰一攞車開車已經跌<br />\n但已經無時間，夾硬要去考官果度，完全無時間熱身<br />\n對腳震到單缸車上到10000轉咁<br />\n結果第二個8字就衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後同阿sir吹水<br />\n佢就教我下次如果條友再唔肯比可以屌鳩佢<br />\n結果我下一次考屌爆佢真係有返(A)<br />\n跟住pass咗"},{"pid":"a858e74b10bccdd23c5a6b62c9d88c3680d96719","tid":520432,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e5ee1fb54ee1b519abc3f5732141f9c718f4f8a","tid":520432,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-0